title: FCP FX - TIFFEN DFX
description:
INFO: http://www.tiffen.com/dfx_v2_image_gallery.htm

FOR FCP 6!

*********************** INSTALL ************************

Install the pkg file as per normal.    Run Tiffen DFX v2

The activation system will come up.

Run FCP.

Select Activate Dfx

Enter Dfx product code: ABCD-ABCD-ABCD-ABCD-ABCD

Select Telephone Activation

Enter any 11 digit Activation Code

The package has been activated.   Do not register with them and do not allow fxtool to connect to tiffen.softwareactivate.com if it tries.  (little snitch
